enst als ein an sich unbestrittenes, aber dennoch heftig umstrittenes Geschäft mit eigener ökonomischen Logik fassbar.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aHistoryxHistorical PeriodsxModern History. 0aSwiss mercenarieszSwitzerlandzLucernexEconomic conditionsy16th century. 0aSwiss mercenarieszSwitzerlandzLucernexHistoryy16th century. 0aSwiss mercenarieszSwitzerlandzLucernexSocial conditionsy16th century. 7aHISTORY / Modern / General.2bisacsh  aLuzern, Militärgeschichte, Schweiz, Sold, Söldner.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2015z9783110438635oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783412218638423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783412218638.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2015  aZDB-23-DGGb2015